---

 About This Project

This project is a multi-feature web application developed using Flask, where I combined:

- A modern Calculator
-  A dynamic Music Player

The goal of this project was to practice full-stack development by integrating frontend (HTML, CSS, JS) with backend (Flask) and handling real-world issues like routing, static files, and debugging.

---

What This Project Shows About Me

- ✔ Ability to build end-to-end web applications
- ✔ Strong understanding of Flask & routing
- ✔ Experience with debugging real errors (Jinja, paths, static files)
- ✔ Frontend + Backend integration skills
- ✔ Problem-solving mindset 

---

-  Calculator – A stylish and interactive calculator UI
-  Music Player – A dynamic music player with playlist support

The project demonstrates full-stack fundamentals including frontend UI, backend routing, and static asset management.

---

 Features

     Calculator

        - Responsive UI design
        - Basic arithmetic operations
        - Clean and modern layout

     Music Player

        - Playlist-based audio system
        - Play / Pause / Next / Previous controls
        - Volume control slider
        - Dynamic song switching

---
Tech Stack

    Technology| Usage
    Python (Flask)| Backend & Routing
    HTML| Structure
    CSS| Styling & UI
    JavaScript| Logic & Interactivity

