⚙️ Installation & Setup

1️.) Clone the repository

git clone <your-repo-link>

2️.) Navigate to project folder

cd myapp

3️.) Install dependencies

pip install flask

4️.) Run the app

python app.py

---

Usage

    Open browser and visit:

http://127.0.0.1:5000

- Click Calculator → Opens calculator page
- Click Music Player → Opens music player

